---
title: Pecan-Crusted Roasted Jumbo Salmon with Creamy Sweet Potato Mash and Broccolini
description: Making pecan-crusted salmon is surprisingly quick and easy when you follow our simple steps. Your final product will be savoury, crunchy salmon fillets with creamy sweet potato mash and broccolini studded with cranberries.

